      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DON'T TELL TOMMY (1) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by a neck at this track in a handy 34.94. Nicely placed here on the inside and has a good record over this journey. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. ADHANA KEVIN (6) is unbeaten over this track and trip in three starts. In the money last time at Hobart (26.00) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 8 length third. Can feature in the finish. STIPULATED (2) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 30.20. Fair draw can see a good run and in form and has the ability. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. PRISTINE (7) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
